title: I have a Pixel 2. I want to download all my photos to my computer desktop. I have thousands on my pi
content: I have a Pixel 2. I want to download all my photos to my computer desktop. I have thousands on my pixel phone. I have tried email and can only get about 3-4 photos to show on each email. I have tried photos.google.com and not all my photos are showing in the site. The most recent are not there. I checked my settings and app and it says I have it shared. Any suggestions?
